snippet: Rookie Marco Gonzales struck out nine, Jhonny Peralta homered and the NL Central-leading St. Louis Cardinals beat the Colorado Rockies 4-1 Sunday for their third straight win....

headline.print_headline: Gonzales, Cardinals Top Rockies for 3rd Win in Row
headline.main: Gonzales, Cardinals Top Rockies for 3rd Win in Row

lead_paragraph: Rookie Marco Gonzales struck out nine, Jhonny Peralta homered and the NL Central-leading St. Louis Cardinals beat the Colorado Rockies 4-1 Sunday for their third straight win.
